data.description: Live the good life (La Buena Vida), in this wonderful 4 bedroom 3 and a 1/2 bath home with room for 3 cars in the oversized garage plus work/gym area! Located on .5 acres of a previous golf course, this fully landscaped yard features room for a large RV, circular driveway, and a large private back yard. Home has separate formal living room, family room, dining room and a dining nook off of the large nicely equipped kitchen. Price to sell so come and see this beauty soon! Sale of this home is contingent on Sellers successful purchase of a home in Smith Valley. Agents are hereby noticed that the home has and active security/monitoring system that may or may not be recording.
